    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Introduction"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We need to think of an Multi Core solution for INC since few customers want INC over SPI at 10Mbps"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Also in few projects, INC module was the one who took most of the CPU time causing CPU load issues"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Below are the proposal for INC in Multicore"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Proposal 1:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Since Inc is in am QM path, we can have masters of IncTp and IncRouter modules to run Core 3 (Non-lockstep CPU)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "And respective Satellite can run in other cores (Core 0 and Core 1)"
    },
